[p 
	"From the opposite side of the usual formula of breaking a game to reach the credits as fast as possible, 
	(__wikiLink|user:Saturn)
	" finishes 
	[em 
		"Chrono Trigger
	]em
	" in a single pass while trying to get as much done as possible without glitching the game out and spending too much time grinding. Consequently this video actually looks like an otherwise normal playthrough by an extremely skilled player.
	$LF
